<ab facs="#facs_190_r1l18">ſache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ıht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het So <expan>vvolte<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
