<del rend="strikethrough">s </del> vnd ſich an <expan>freuntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> rehten vor des <expan>R<ex>eichs</ex></expan> <expan>Rıht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns cʒu </ab>
